@node _open_r
@section @code{_open_r}---Reentrant version of open
@findex _open_r
@strong{Synopsis}
@example
#include <reent.h>
int _open_r(struct _reent *@var{ptr},
    const char *@var{file}, int @var{flags}, int @var{mode});

@end example
@strong{Description}@*
This is a reentrant version of @code{open}.  It
takes a pointer to the global data block, which holds
@code{errno}.

